        <div2>
          <head>
            <title type="main">
              <hi rend="i">Blake at the Oscars</hi>
            </title>
          </head>
          <p>Sunday, 21 March 1999—Roberto Benigni, accepting the Academy Award for Best Foreign Film for
<hi rend="i">Life is Beautiful</hi> quoted Blake: “He who kisses the joy as it flies, lives in Eternity’s
sunrise.”</p>
        </div2>
